preambule.al:
The Government of the Kingdom of the Netherlands and the Government
of the Republic of South Africa (hereinafter jointly referred to as
‘‘the Parties’’ and in the singular as ‘‘a Party’’);

Considering that military and civilian personnel of the Department /
Ministry of Defence of the Parties will be present in each other’s territory
for activities related to military cooperation;

li.al:
‘‘Dependent’’ means the spouse of a member of the Personnel of the
Sending State or a child of such member depending on him or her for
support;

